<p style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:
0in'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;color:black'>Pathological hair
loss on the head and body up to their complete disappearance (baldness) is
called alopecia.</span></p>

<p style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:
0in'><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:18.0pt;color:black'>Do I need
